<p><img alt="Good Fit Graphic Tool" height="250" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Online Learning/OD/Good-Fit-Tool-(New).gif" width="720" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">1. To qualify to apply for an online degree, you must:</p>
<ul>
<li>be in good academic and financial standing at all institutions previously attended.</li>
<li>have completed a minimum of 15 credits with a 3.0 GPA, or 30 credits with a 2.0 GPA, from Ricks College, BYU-Idaho, LDS Business College, BYU, Pathway, or BYU-Hawaii (if you have credits from two or more of these institutions that meet the credit totals and GPA requirements, you may also qualify).</li>
<li>Commit to the BYU-Idaho Honor Code and maintain annual ecclesiastical endorsements.</li>
</ul>
<p>2. Determine which degree you are interested in by reviewing the different <a href="x42518.xml" target="_blank">degree sites</a>. Make sure to check when upper-division courses in that degree <a href="x33948.xml">become available</a> and when you would need them. This is still a very new program, and availability dates for courses and majors vary widely.</p>
<p><img name="Fit 3" />3. Review your transcript, on <a href="https://my.byui.edu/ICS/">my.byui.edu</a> if you have attended BYU-Idaho or wherever it might be found at other institutions, and see if any of the coursework you have already completed will fulfill requirements for the degree you have selected.</p>
<p><img name="Fit 4" />4. If you believe that an online degree from BYU-Idaho is the right choice for you, proceed with the <a href="x24381.xml">application process</a>.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded=""><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="x18360" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x17147" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="SiteControl" Expanded="false"/></Content>
